---
title: Tuscan-Style Pork Tenderloin with Herb-Tomato Sauce & Roasted Baby Potatoes
description: Tender perfection, roasted and flavourful, that’s how people will be describing this dinner. Seasoned pork is only the beginning of this dish's magic. Paired with a rich tomato sauce, peppered with pine nuts and feta, and served with classic roasted potatoes, this will have the aftertaste of satisfaction. It’s a five-star experience!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
